Colouration
[in ethanol]. Reddish brown, prosoma with transverse dark lines leading to fovea, dorsal opisthosoma with series of large chevrons at proximal end turning smaller gradually at distal end, legs clearly banded (
Figs 49a–b
); ventral opisthosoma with a uniform compact dark marking below epigastric furrow (
Fig. 49b
).
